{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Embark on the Adventure: Chip &amp; Sparky Demo</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the beginning of Chip's journey in the <strong>Chip &amp; Sparky Demo</strong>, where you\u2019ll play through the <strong>first level</strong> of this exciting 3D action platformer! Take on the role of Chip, a young robot working in his uncle Rusty\u2019s shop. When a mysterious ship raids the shop and leaves Rusty injured, Chip is thrown into action to recover a stolen invention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>What\u2019s Included in the Demo:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore the First Level:</strong> Dive into the bustling town and Rusty\u2019s workshop as you get a taste of the game\u2019s vibrant world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Core Platforming Gameplay:</strong> Run, jump, and dash across obstacles while battling enemies and uncovering hidden secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Early Gadgets and Abilities:</strong> Try out Chip's starter abilities and gadgets that will help you navigate the level and fend off foes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Engage with Sparky:</strong> Get introduced to Chip\u2019s loyal sidekick, Sparky, and see how the duo begins to work together.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This demo provides a sneak peek of the full game, giving you a taste of its action-packed platforming, unique gadgets, and dynamic characters. Ready to join Chip and Sparky on their journey?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341560/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736734211","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341560/page.bg.jpg?t=1736734211","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341560/49642e3443fb31016706e6d4a9568b15c59d639f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736734211","